Class Teacher

  • java.lang.Object
    • FileDialog.Teacher
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable

    public class Teacher
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable
    The Teacher class represents a teacher with a name, class, room, and date. This class implements the Comparable interface to allow for sorting by teacher name.

        public int compareTo(java.lang.Object o)
